data.description: Welcome to this move-in ready, paired home located in Homestead Hills! This alluring 3-bedroom, 2 ½ bath home is a testament to modern comfort and style. Offering a perfect blend of contemporary design elements and efficient use of space. The heart of the home is the open concept living area where kitchen, living and dining rooms seamlessly flow together, ideal for everyday living and entertaining. Enjoy your cozy private outdoor living space easily accessed from the dining room. The unfinished basement is a blank canvas awaiting your personal touch. Experience the convenience and accessibility to local amenities, parks, and trails. LOW monthly HOA! Don’t miss an opportunity to see this beautiful home!
